                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Mengucapkan alhamdulilah,melaksanakan nazar jika ada</p><p></p><p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>Mengucap  kalimat hamdalah</p><p></p><p><strong>Alhamdulillah</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>.</strong><strong> </strong></p><p>Semoga<strong> </strong>membantu....</p><br />
